Class EntityNetworkSearchNode

  • java.lang.Object

    • Constructor Detail

      • EntityNetworkSearchNode

        public EntityNetworkSearchNode(String nodeId,
                               SearchNode searchNode,
                               boolean isOutputEnabled,
                               List<String> disabledFilterInfoIds)
        Constructs a new EntityNetworkSearchNode, initializing all mandatory fields.
        Parameters:
        nodeId - A String containing an identifier for this EntityNetworkSearchNode that must be unique within the network of nodes.
        searchNode - The SearchNode that this EntityNetworkSearchNode contains.
        isOutputEnabled - true if Entitys that matched this NetworkSearchNode should be included in the network search results; false otherwise.
        disabledFilterInfoIds - Strings identifying FilterInfos within the SearchNode that will not be applied when the network search involving this EntityNetworkSearchNode takes place.
